def strandCount(strandString):
    #create an empty dictionary
    dict = {}
    for i in range(len(strandString)):
        if (strandString[i] in dict):
            dict[strandString[i]] += 1
        else:
            dict[strandString[i]] = 1
    for i in dict:
        print(f'{i} - {dict[i]}')
